---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Academics - Erfan Ramezani | Teaching & Research";
const description = "Erfan Ramezani's academic contributions, teaching assistant experience, research work, and professional certifications in AI and computer engineering.";
const canonicalURL = "https://erfan-ramezani.ir/academics";
---

<MainLayout 
  title={title} 
  description={description} 
  canonicalURL={canonicalURL}
  currentPage="academics"
>
  <article class="Recommendations active" data-page="academics">
    <header>
      <h2 class="h2 article-title">Academics</h2>
    </header>

    <section class="recommendations-content">
      <div class="recommendations-section">
        <h3 class="h3 section-title">Academic Recommendations</h3>
        
        <div class="recommendation-list-gallery">
          <div class="recommendation-card">
            <div class="recommendation-card-header">
              <img src="/assets/images/norouzi.jpeg" alt="Dr. Mohammad Norouzi" class="recommendation-card-avatar">
              <div class="recommendation-card-info">
                <h4 class="h4 recommendation-title">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohammad-norouzi-617ba573" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="recommendation-link">Dr. Mohammad Norouzi</a>
                </h4>
                <p class="recommendation-position">Assistant Professor and Director at MRL (Mechatronics Research Laboratory), Qazvin Azad University, Iran</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="recommendation-text">
              "Erfan has been an exceptional member of our research team at MRL. His deep understanding of AI concepts and robotics integration, combined with his innovative approach to problem-solving, makes him stand out as a researcher and developer."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="recommendation-card">
            <div class="recommendation-card-header">
              <img src="/assets/images/zeinali.jpeg" alt="Prof. Esmaeil Zeinali" class="recommendation-card-avatar">
              <div class="recommendation-card-info">
                <h4 class="h4 recommendation-title">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/esmaeil-zeinali-b12a932ab" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="recommendation-link">Prof. Esmaeil Zeinali</a>
                </h4>
                <p class="recommendation-position">Associate Professor at Qazvin Islamic Azad University</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="recommendation-text">
              "As Erfan's professor and academic advisor, I have witnessed his exceptional dedication to learning and teaching. His performance as a teaching assistant and his contributions to our Computer Architecture course have been outstanding. He demonstrates remarkable ability in explaining complex technical concepts to students."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="recommendation-card">
            <div class="recommendation-card-header">
              <div class="recommendation-card-icon">
                <ion-icon name="business-outline"></ion-icon>
              </div>
              <div class="recommendation-card-info">
                <h4 class="h4 recommendation-title">Industry Recommendation</h4>
                <p class="recommendation-position">MRL Robotics Lab</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="recommendation-text">
              "Erfan's leadership in AI development and his innovative approach to robotics integration have been instrumental in advancing our research projects. His expertise in LLM integration with robotic systems sets him apart in the field."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="teaching-section">
        <h3 class="h3 section-title">Teaching Assistant Experience</h3>
        
        <div class="teaching-list">
          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="school-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">Digital Systems and Design</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">Dr. Mohammad Hamghalam</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Teaching assistant for Digital Systems and Design course, helping students understand digital logic, circuit design, and hardware description languages.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="school-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">Compiler Design</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">Dr. Fardin Shapouri</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Teaching assistant for Compiler Design course, assisting students with lexical analysis, parsing, code generation, and optimization techniques.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="school-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">Electrical Circuits</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">Prof. Saeed Haji-Nasiri</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Teaching assistant for Electrical Circuits course, supporting students in understanding circuit analysis, AC/DC circuits, and electrical components.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="school-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">Computer Architecture</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">Prof. Esmaeil Zeinali</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Teaching assistant for Computer Architecture course, helping students grasp processor design, memory systems, and computer organization principles.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h3 class="h3 section-title">Academic & Research Gallery</h3>
        
        <div class="recommendations-gallery">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1744858680330.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1744859632126.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1757345726623.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1757346880727.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1757423172087.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1757423281487.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Recommendations/1759335036581.jpeg" alt="Academic Research Photo" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="certificates-section">
        <h3 class="h3 section-title">Certificates & Professional Development</h3>
        
        <div class="teaching-list">
          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="school-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">DeepLearning.AI Specializations</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">Online Courses - deeplearning.ai</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Completed multiple specializations in deep learning, machine learning, and AI through DeepLearning.AI platform, covering neural networks, CNNs, RNNs, NLP, and practical AI applications.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="teaching-item">
            <div class="teaching-icon">
              <ion-icon name="trophy-outline"></ion-icon>
            </div>
            <div class="teaching-content">
              <h4 class="h4 teaching-title">UC Berkeley LLM Agents MOOC</h4>
              <span class="teaching-duration">University of California, Berkeley</span>
              <p class="teaching-description">
                Advanced course on Large Language Model agents, multi-agent reasoning, theorem proving, and autoformalization from UC Berkeley.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h3 class="h3 section-title">Certificate Gallery</h3>
        
        <div class="recommendations-gallery">
          <img src="/assets/images/Certificates/Coursera.jpg" alt="Coursera Certificate" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
          <img src="/assets/images/Certificates/advllmagentssp25.jpg" alt="Advanced LLM Agents Certificate" class="gallery-image recommendations-gallery-img">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
